00:33:54,628 --> 00:33:55,769
É aqui que estamos.

707
00:33:56,131 --> 00:33:57,131
Alex?

708
00:33:57,590 --> 00:33:58,590
Ryan?

709
00:33:58,834 --> 00:34:01,512
